# --- project-specific exclusions (per request) ------------------------------
# Large prescribed inputs (HITRAN 2020, AFGL profile, CU solar spectrum)
data/
# All simulation output (chunk files, per-band + merged HDF5, absorption cache)
out/
# Operating-rules file (kept local, not committed)
CLAUDE.md

# --- scientific data-format files (generated / bulky / provided separately) -
